overview: We at “Yalla Orient tours Inc,” take pride in our knowledge of each of our destinations. Our years of experience, proven logistical capabilities, and exceptional knowledge of the most remote areas and cultures makes “Yalla Orient tours Inc” the ideal company to assist you in your journey. Our contacts among the peoples of our destinations, and the scientists who work in each of them, make each of our unique trips a very special and exciting experience.
